 People walk past a floral installation during the Fleurs de Villes Noel floral exhibition in Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada, on Dec. 11, 2021. The outdoor floral exhibition Fleurs de Villes Noel is presented in Vancouver from Dec. 10 to Dec. 19, featuring more than 40 pop-up installations created by local florists. (Photo by Liang Sen/Xinhua)  A man looks at a floral installation during the Fleurs de Villes Noel floral exhibition in Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada, on Dec. 11, 2021. The outdoor floral exhibition Fleurs de Villes Noel is presented in Vancouver from Dec. 10 to Dec. 19, featuring more than 40 pop-up installations created by local florists. (Photo by Liang Sen/Xinhua)  A woman looks at a floral installation during the Fleurs de Villes Noel floral exhibition in Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada, on Dec. 11, 2021. The outdoor floral exhibition Fleurs de Villes Noel is presented in Vancouver from Dec. 10 to Dec. 19, featuring more than 40 pop-up installations created by local florists. (Photo by Liang Sen/Xinhua)  People look at a floral installation during the Fleurs de Villes Noel floral exhibition in Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada, on Dec. 11, 2021. The outdoor floral exhibition Fleurs de Villes Noel is presented in Vancouver from Dec. 10 to Dec. 19, featuring more than 40 pop-up installations created by local florists. (Photo by Liang Sen/Xinhua)  People walk past a floral installation during the Fleurs de Villes Noel floral exhibition in Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada, on Dec. 11, 2021. The outdoor floral exhibition Fleurs de Villes Noel is presented in Vancouver from Dec. 10 to Dec. 19, featuring more than 40 pop-up installations created by local florists. (Photo by Liang Sen/Xinhua)